History tab is simply a 'history' of the changes made to the item since its creation (including original values)
Its content is loaded when clicked the tab, to save time on whole form loading.

[emph]Data stored[/emph]

For each row of data it is shown the following info:

  Date: date and time when the change was done (or creation, the first time). 
  User: who made it.
  Field: what field of the item it applies to.
  Old value: previous value (except for item creation).
  New value: new value.
  